{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc3a3c3c75","title":"应集结主力歼灭敌三十五军","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8fd537fc7a","index":0,"year":1948,"month":4,"day":4,"articleId":"fc3a3c3c75"}],"tags":[{"id":"607fc161b8","name":"杨得志","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"79f3daaaa7","type":"paragraph","text":"应集结主力歼灭敌三十五军","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"fc3a3c3c75"},{"id":"fbe27676aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年4月4日）杨、罗、杨、耿，并告楚、萧，中工委三日电委。你们应集结主力歼灭西援之三十五军，然后继续在绥远”扩张，吸引东敌西接，各个击灭之","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"fc3a3c3c75"},{"id":"bebe79ae47","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"fc3a3c3c75"},{"id":"6614b19bc7","type":"paragraph","text":"四日二十四时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给香察翼野战军司令员杨得志、第一政治委员罗瑞脚、第二政治委员杨成武和参谋长就照的电藏12]泵、萧，指最荣臻、萧克，当时分别任晋息军区司令员莱政治委[3]指1948年4月3日杨得志、罗瑞卿给中共中央军委的电报。电报说：“我们提议以下两个作战方案：（一）以主力出缓运作夺取全经远的计划。（二）一、六队打下凉城后即以一部围大同，主力美中打摄，如援不好打则出平缓东段。”[4]绥远，旧省名，韩今内蒙吉自治区中部地区，1954年撤销。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"fc3a3c3c75"}],"page":{"id":"e8a822533b","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"fc3a3c3c75","start":216,"end":216}}}},"__N_SSG":true}